===Etymology=== 
LL prisma, sawn to shape
===Noun===
# (Maths) A [[polyhedron]] in with parallel ends of the same size and shape, with the other faces being [[parallelogram||parallelograms]]-shaped sides.
# A transparent block in the shape of a prism (typically with triangular ends), used to split or reflect light.
# A crystal in which the faces are parallel to the vertical axis.
